**c.**
```python
from scipy.interpolate import lagrange, interp1d

x = np.linspace(0,2*np.pi, 100)

x1 = array([0., np.pi/2, np.pi, 3*np.pi/2, 2*np.pi])
x2 = np.linspace(0, 2*np.pi, 10)
